    "text_2": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "AIR ZOOM VICTORY TOUR 3 NRG",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h4><strong>Design & Features</strong></h4><p>The Air Zoom Victory Tour 3 NRG is crafted with a breathable textile upper, ensuring that golfers' feet stay cool and comfortable throughout their rounds. The shoe features Tour Flex Pro SoftSpikes under the forefoot and Silver Tornado spikes in the lateral and heel areas, providing increased stability and traction. This combination ensures that golfers can maintain their footing on various terrains, which is essential for those critical shots.</p><h4><strong>Performance & Comfort</strong></h4><p>Designed with elite athletes in mind, the Air Zoom Victory Tour 3 NRG offers exceptional performance on the course. The breathable textile helps manage moisture, keeping feet dry even in warmer conditions. The strategic placement of spikes ensures optimal grip and stability, allowing golfers to confidently execute their swings. The classic design, complemented by the sky-blue accents, makes this shoe a stylish choice for any golfer.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
