    "text_3": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "AIR PEGASUS '89 G NRG",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h4><strong>Design & Features</strong></h4><p>The Air Pegasus '89 G NRG combines the iconic silhouette of the original Air Pegasus '89 with modern golf shoe technology. This model features a hidden air unit in the heel for extra cushioning, a soft terry cloth tongue and collar lining, and a grippy rubber outsole. The sky blue, waterproof exterior is stylish and practical, keeping feet dry in various weather conditions.</p><h4><strong>Performance & Comfort</strong></h4><p>While the Air Pegasus '89 G NRG is designed for casual golfers, it doesn't compromise on performance. The hidden Zoom Air unit in the heel provides responsive cushioning, making each step comfortable. The grippy rubber outsole offers excellent traction, ensuring stability across different surfaces. This shoe is perfect for golfers who appreciate a blend of vintage design and modern functionality.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
