    "text_4": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "AIR ZOOM INFINITY TOUR NRG",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h4><strong>Design & Features</strong></h4><p>The Air Zoom Infinity Tour NRG features a breathable textile upper and plenty of lateral support, making it ideal for high-performance play. The Air Zoom unit in the forefoot is designed to move with your feet as you swing, enhancing energy transfer from the ground to your shot. This shoe's design is inspired by previous Nike models like the Air Max 1 and 90 G, known for their performance and style.</p><h4><strong>Performance & Comfort</strong></h4><p>The Air Zoom Infinity Tour NRG is all about optimising energy transfer and providing stability. The forefoot Zoom Air unit ensures that each swing is powered by a responsive energy return, giving golfers an edge in their game. The breathable upper and lateral support make this shoe comfortable for extended wear, whether on the course or the driving range.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
