    "text_5": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Special Edition NRG Theme: \"Accept and Embrace\"",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>For the US Open at Pinehurst No. 2, Nike has introduced the \"Accept and Embrace\" theme for the Pegasus '89. This theme draws inspiration from North Carolina, incorporating shades of dark and light blue reminiscent of Michael Jordan's alma mater. The variety of textures used in the design, from hairy and smooth suede to soft terry cloth, adds a rich, tactile dimension to the shoes. The words \"Accept\" and \"Embrace\" are featured on the tongue labels, shoelace ends, and insoles, emphasising the theme.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
