        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>All these models are now available on <a href=\"https://trendygolf.com/\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">TRENDYGOLF.COM</span></a>, just in time for the US Open Championship 2024. Whether you are an elite athlete or a casual golfer, Nike's new line of NRG golf shoes offers something for everyone. With their blend of performance, comfort, and style, these shoes are set to make a statement on the greens of Pinehurst No. 2.</p><p>In conclusion, Nike's Summer 2024 US Open NRG Golf Shoes are a testament to the brand's commitment to innovation and style. From the high-performance Air Zoom Victory Tour 3 NRG to the vintage-inspired Air Pegasus '89 G NRG, each model offers unique features tailored to different types of golfers. Whether you are drawn to the \"Accept and Embrace\" theme or the advanced technology of the Air Zoom Infinity Tour NEXT%, there is a pair that will meet your needs and elevate your game. Don't miss out on these limited-edition shoes that celebrate the spirit of the US Open and the rich heritage of Pinehurst No. 2.</p>"
          }
        },
